Author: adrawnangel
Text: I'm trying to convince myself of that - that surely it'll even out, especially with the low intakes from earlier, but of course my anxious brain defies logic all the time  You're incredibly sweet, thank you ❤️

Author: strangernumberone
Text: Sometimes when I do that while restricting, my stomach revolts and I end up losing weight in a day or so. You're not a failure for allowing yourself some pasta though.❤
